bunching_leaderboard.query:
SELECT trip_log.rt, trip_log.v, trip_log.pid, trip_log.trip_id, scheduledstop_log.stop_id, scheduledstop_log.stop_name, scheduledstop_log.arrival_timestamp 
FROM trip_log JOIN scheduledstop_log ON trip_log.trip_id = scheduledstop_log.trip_id 
WHERE trip_log.rt = :rt_1 AND scheduledstop_log.stop_id = :stop_id_1 AND scheduledstop_log.arrival_timestamp IS NOT NULL AND scheduledstop_log.arrival_timestamp IS NOT NULL AND scheduledstop_log.arrival_timestamp >= ADDDATE(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, INTERVAL -1 DAY) ORDER BY scheduledstop_log.arrival_timestamp ASC
